title: RESET_MAPDATA_ENTITY_MATRIX

0x8143FA4F// ResetMapdataEntityMatrix
BOOL RESET_MAPDATA_ENTITY_MATRIX(int mapDataHash, int entityInternalIdx);Parameters:mapDataHash: A mapdata hash from mapDataLoaded event.entityInternalIdx: An internal entity's index.Returns: True if successful, false if not.Resets mapdata entity transform matrix to its original state.
This function supports SDK infrastructure and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
